collections.name: Timecoin REALITY VS DENIAL - Each piece and collections are unique
collections.description:
REALITY vs DENIAL

26 NFT Timecoins collection, featuring the most significant time moments.

Not a battle of right vs. wrong. Not truth vs. lies. This is about the human experience of perception and choice.

We pour effort into something—relationships, ambitions, even daily tasks—but reality doesn’t always align with what we envisioned. Fatigue sets in, expectations bend, and at some point, we adjust, reinterpret, or outright deny. We tell ourselves “it’s fine” when we know it’s not. We look the other way. We balance between truth and denial, sometimes embracing reality, sometimes rewriting it.

Denial isn’t just avoidance—it’s a tool. A pause. A coping mechanism. Sometimes it buys time, sometimes it holds us back. This Timecoin is a mirror of that universal moment—the inner conflict, the decision to see or unsee, the choice to move forward or stay in limbo.

The open eye sees. The closed eye chooses not to. Truth and denial are two sides of the same coin.

collections.description:
Lonely Men Collection - A Journey Through Solitude and Mystery

The Lonely Men collection is a visual exploration of solitude, mystery, and the connection between man and the vast unknown. Each artwork captures a lone silhouette standing at the edge of breathtaking landscapes - forgotten ruins, endless deserts, cosmic horizons, and surreal dreamscapes.

These figures, faceless yet full of meaning, are more than wanderers; they are silent observers of time, lost between worlds, standing in places where history, nature, and the universe intertwine. Every piece tells a story of isolation, introspection, and the beauty of unknown.

Where at the edge of a crumbling bridge, beneath a sky filled with infinite stars, or gazing upon the ruins of civilizations long past, the Lonely Men remind us that in solitude, there is wonder. In the silence, there is depth. And in the unknown, there is endless possibility.

Welcome to the Lonely Men Collection - a journey through the extraordinary.

Each album has a distinct visual style, merging metallic relic aesthetics, biomechanical elements, and ethereal lighting for a timeless experience. Whether as a tribute to faith, a reflection on human nature, or a bold artistic vision, it reinterprets the apostles’ legacy through a modern, cinematic lens.

Crafted by Radim Kacer, this exclusive digital artwork series is designed for collectors, art enthusiasts, and those seeking a deeper visual connection to biblical history. Immerse yourself in the mystery, sacrifice, and destiny of the Twelve.
